data.description: If you need a bedroom downstairs, The Palmetto II is a FAMILY favorite! Formal dining with trey ceiling is perfect for large families during the holidays! The kitchen is gorgeous with stainless steel appliances, granite counters and stunning cabinets. Kitchen and family room are all open to each other. Master features large walk in closet and beautiful ensuite with dual vanity, garden tub and separate shower. Spacious bonus room and laundry upstairs! Wedgefield is located close to Fort Bragg, Fayetteville and easy access to I-295 / I-95.
